Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜同學怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起平常好有壓迫感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 他正發愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發愁？ 出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 少女般的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(362,55)}{\pos(127,180)\shad0\fad(480,0)\c&HAC78EE&}少女般的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是關於禮物的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 白色情人節已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馬上就是春假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有什麼能讓小紅開心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在白夜能做到的範圍內就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}豪華的東西反而會讓人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(542,0)\shad0\3c&H9A4A4B&\frz344.314\c&H2B2226&\move(967,423,990,366,27,5615)\shad0\3c&H9A4A4B&}不\N用\N勉\N強
