Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是讓你更沒頭緒了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那又是我們兩個一起回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…話題話題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}瀏海 不礙事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遮著眼睛不礙事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這倒是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣也挺好的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅平時也很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要好好回禮才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本來是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果不知不覺全都買成巧克力蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}路上沒人 走近路好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正傍晚也容易混過去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 剛才有誰在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有人在的吧 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}沒、沒 、沒有暴露…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到飛行類人生物了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}飛行類人生物？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被別人看到你那樣很不好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還是被大野同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我本來想著都傍晚了應該沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孩子傍晚一個人走在街上也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為遇到怪人或者被捲入犯罪事件就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2E177D&\fad(417,0)\move(62,459,62,421,29,1614)\3c&HBAB0F7&\shad0}犯\N罪\N事\N件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\c&H2E177D&\fad(417,0)\move(1213,356,1213,397,29,1614)\3c&HBAB0F7&}怪\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經完全被當作那類人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白 白夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到真白碳哭著跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 稍微被白夜訓斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳被訓斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擊 心碎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 現在就是趁虛而入的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}問我幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以後會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密暴露了我也不好住這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遇到了怪人就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密暴露了就不能住城裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰白夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰真白同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎、怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 比想像中的還要悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然高中的學習太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這沒辦法囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為實際上是上小學的年紀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}數學成績提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多虧小紅教我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜同學成績不也是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為很聰明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}意外的好像不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像還沒想到送什麼禮物的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 還在煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬 成績怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不是問這個的時候啊 木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到了 我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA 那絕對是飛行類人生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}飛行類人生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像人類一樣的東西在屋頂飛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那絕對是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人外生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未確認生物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸 嘿……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬看到的難道是那個小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的我已經是這邊的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會再變回過去的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}「這邊」是哪邊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的取材暫時放過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為有更好的題材了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會給小紅添麻煩了倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為有更好的題材了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不會找小紅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2F2C33&\shad0\move(226,533,247,533,0,2234)}怎\N麼\N說\N才\N好\N呢   \N\N說\N不\N出\N口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我認為小紅是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然間說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擾了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼說我真是礙事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的就是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又…又不是因為我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我尊敬的可是紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隨你們搞好關係就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}約會之類的全部都搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相親相愛就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然我不喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那個想法可以有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}約會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然是白夜請客
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是這麼多尼斯湖水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個零食公司對尼斯湖水怪有什麼樣的執著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}關於明天那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白有什麼想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 那是你們兩個去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想真白可能也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在一想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像一直都沒有帶你們參觀過這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼先想一想想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是電燈泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅不會把真白放家裡然後去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是說你想要一個人在家裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}絕對要帶我去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}電影？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也可以不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為是春假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各種小孩子的電影也在上映
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這個
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H68EAF1&\3c&H2B2D41&\shad0\frz24.461\pos(14,237)\fad(400,0)}我的兒子\N被宇宙人抓走\N很頭痛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 大家要出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天沒機會告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒 快一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天要去幫忙義賣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幫忙幼稚園慈善拍賣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是要早點去然後做準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等… 為什麼變成那樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微有點晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是白色情人節的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是所謂的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶著小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是普通的去玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐不同意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是去看電影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒有帶白夜和真白在這附近玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我不高興所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}準備讓我等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不同意的啊！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是抱歉 姐姐大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如說從沒想過能瞞過她出門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也覺得看電影就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 有約會的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是、是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是這一部…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要開始了哦
