Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好、好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兒子太強了嚇人一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明那麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼被抓走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸爸只是在困惑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吧 很有意思吧 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…最後被宇宙人被用球棒打的時候很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}音樂有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺今天氣氛有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅去約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}with真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說 要好好工作啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
