Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夜之森 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被人這樣稱呼會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像是 姐姐 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐潔大人 姐碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那麼害怕宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是看電影就沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是因為害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要做好萬一被襲擊時候的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以要知己知彼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是電影是虛構的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}需購？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好漂亮啊 好多春天的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白你們住的山上也會有好多花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 雪應該融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好也是可以上山採野菜的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 已經可以採野菜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}土當歸啊 水芹啊 蜂斗菜藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有只有在我們山上才能採到的野菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好呢 我好想用那些做些料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真是好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到好多初春的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午餐那盤蛋包飯很不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz252.216\fad(300,0)\fn@華康粗圓體\shad0\c&HCB357E&\an7\bord1.5\blur1\3c&H581D3B&\pos(1218,59)}味道太濃\N\N雞蛋也該再鬆軟一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在外面吃飯主要是享受氣氛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}起風了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那晚飯吃點熱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 今天都只去了真白想去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒約會就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起約會今天就算是出來玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都怪我太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的 下回再去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是、是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好大的風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}傷痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…傷痕是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是看到了什麼異常現象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因為等離子體的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我聽不懂日語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本沒吹出聲啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個傷痕…果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前 因為我的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我笨笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨笨的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是這樣的 白夜是笨笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總是冒冒失失的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 不用再隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼想都是為了救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我做事不周全才受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能怪小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我當時再做的好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不會讓小紅受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為好擔心 所以我來接你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經四點了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要變成不良了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邁向不良的第一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才四點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是你們沒事就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開 開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臉色好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請你不要在意白夜的傷痕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜最想避免的就是小紅因此而煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以要是為白夜著想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就請不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然說了要她別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但還是會介意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟也是突發狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我算是先給家裡告知了一下事情經過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老家來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒睡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已經春假了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微睡過頭一點也沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 差不多該起床了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早飯已經做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 行李不見了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ED
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未確認進行式 下週最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟真白碳一起洗澡游泳真是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請不要隨意捏造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要小紅在身邊我怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白嗎？ 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被搶詞了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
